Note:
Runa Scientific Computing: Optimization Core (Compatibility Layer)

This is a compatibility wrapper that imports from the unified math optimization engine.
All functionality has been moved to math/engine/optimization for better architecture.
:End Note

Import "math/engine/optimization/core" as OptEngine

Note: Re-export optimization types
Type OptimizationResult is OptEngine.OptimizationResult
Type ConvergenceCriteria is OptEngine.ConvergenceCriteria
Type ConstraintType is OptEngine.ConstraintType
Type OptimizationMethod is OptEngine.OptimizationMethod

Note: Re-export unconstrained optimization
Process called "minimize" that takes func as Any and x0 as Any and method as Any returns OptimizationResult:
    Return OptEngine.minimize with func as func and x0 as x0 and method as method

Process called "maximize" that takes func as Any and x0 as Any and method as Any returns OptimizationResult:
    Return OptEngine.maximize with func as func and x0 as x0 and method as method

Note: Re-export constrained optimization
Process called "minimize_constrained" that takes func as Any and x0 as Any and constraints as Any returns OptimizationResult:
    Return OptEngine.minimize_constrained with func as func and x0 as x0 and constraints as constraints

Process called "linear_programming" that takes c as Any and a_ub as Any and b_ub as Any returns OptimizationResult:
    Return OptEngine.linear_programming with c as c and a_ub as a_ub and b_ub as b_ub

Note: Re-export global optimization
Process called "differential_evolution" that takes func as Any and bounds as Any returns OptimizationResult:
    Return OptEngine.differential_evolution with func as func and bounds as bounds

Process called "simulated_annealing" that takes func as Any and x0 as Any and temperature as Any returns OptimizationResult:
    Return OptEngine.simulated_annealing with func as func and x0 as x0 and temperature as temperature

Process called "genetic_algorithm" that takes func as Any and bounds as Any and population_size as Any returns OptimizationResult:
    Return OptEngine.genetic_algorithm with func as func and bounds as bounds and population_size as population_size

Note: Re-export root finding
Process called "find_root" that takes func as Any and x0 as Any and method as Any returns Any:
    Return OptEngine.find_root with func as func and x0 as x0 and method as method

Process called "find_roots" that takes func as Any and bracket as Any returns Any:
    Return OptEngine.find_roots with func as func and bracket as bracket

Note: Re-export curve fitting
Process called "curve_fit" that takes func as Any and xdata as Any and ydata as Any returns OptimizationResult:
    Return OptEngine.curve_fit with func as func and xdata as xdata and ydata as ydata

Process called "least_squares" that takes func as Any and x0 as Any returns OptimizationResult:
    Return OptEngine.least_squares with func as func and x0 as x0